      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained by its sole owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no chips, scratches, or dents, while the interior remains in pristine state with no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Mechanically, the car is perfect; it runs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, with all systems functioning flawlessly and a complete service history provided. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle of this caliber that truly requires nothing but a new driver.",
